    },
    {
      "id": "el_11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 328,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "Pipe fills in a hrs, leak empties in b hrs\nNet time = ab/(b-a)\n\nLeak starts after t hours:\nFilled by pipe in t hrs = t/a\nRemaining = 1 - t/a\nTime for rest = remaining/(1/a - 1/b)\n\nWHY: Before leak, pipe fills alone.\n  After leak, net rate drops to\n  1/a - 1/b. Remaining/net = time.\n\nEx: Pipe=6h, leak after 2h, leak=12h\n  Filled=2/6=1/3. Left=2/3.\n  Net=1/6-1/12=1/12 → 2/3÷1/12=8h",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 11,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pipe fills in a hrs, leak empties in b hrs\nNet time = ab/(b-a)\n\nLeak starts after t hours:\nFilled by pipe in t hrs = t/a\nRemaining = 1 - t/a\nTime for rest = remaining/(1/a - 1/b)\n\nWHY: Before leak, pipe fills alone.\n  After leak, net rate drops to\n  1/a - 1/b. Remaining/net = time.\n\nEx: Pipe=6h, leak after 2h, leak=12h\n  Filled=2/6=1/3. Left=2/3.\n  Net=1/6-1/12=1/12 → 2/3÷1/12=8h",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
