      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 748,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A pipe fills a tank in 8 hours. Due to a leak, it takes 10\nhours. In how many hours can the leak alone empty the full\ntank?",
