      "x": 535,
      "y": 1161,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Pipe A fills 1/3 of a tank in 1 hour. Pipe B fills 1/4 in\n1 hour. A works for 1 hour, then B for 1 hour,\nalternately. How long to fill?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
