    },
    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1242,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/3/hr, B=1/4/hr\n  2-hr cycle: 1/3+1/4 = 7/12\nStep 2: 1 cycle(2h)=7/12, left=5/12\n  Hr3(A): 1/3=4/12, left=1/12\n  Hr4(B): (1/12)÷(1/4)=1/3 hr\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM tank=12 → A=4/hr, B=3/hr\n\n  |H1 |H2 |H3 |H4     |\n  | A | B | A | B(1/3) |\n  | 4 | 3 | 4 | 1      | =12\n  |cycle 1| cycle 2+   |\n\nAfter 2h:7 done. Hr3(A):4→left=1\nHr4(B):1/3 hr → Total=3h 20min\n\nAnswer: 3 hours 20 minutes ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 40,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/3/hr, B=1/4/hr\n  2-hr cycle: 1/3+1/4 = 7/12\nStep 2: 1 cycle(2h)=7/12, left=5/12\n  Hr3(A): 1/3=4/12, left=1/12\n  Hr4(B): (1/12)÷(1/4)=1/3 hr\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM tank=12 → A=4/hr, B=3/hr\n\n  |H1 |H2 |H3 |H4     |\n  | A | B | A | B(1/3) |\n  | 4 | 3 | 4 | 1      | =12\n  |cycle 1| cycle 2+   |\n\nAfter 2h:7 done. Hr3(A):4→left=1\nHr4(B):1/3 hr → Total=3h 20min\n\nAnswer: 3 hours 20 minutes ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
