    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1242,
      "width": 317,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/20/min, B=1/30/min\n  2-min cycle = 1/20+1/30 = 1/12\nStep 2: 11 cycles(22min) = 11/12\n  Left=1/12. Min23(A):1/20\n  After 23: 11/12+1/20=58/60, left=2/60=1/30\n  Min24(B): 1/30 at 1/30 rate = 1 min exact\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM(20,30)=60 → A=3/min, B=2/min\n\n  |M1|M2|M3|M4|...|M23|M24|\n  | A| B| A| B|...| A | B |\n  | 3| 2| 3| 2|...| 3 | 2 |\n  |cycle1|cycle2|  12 cycles=60\n\n12 cycles × 2min = 24 min exact\n\nAnswer: 24 minutes ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 45,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_6"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/20/min, B=1/30/min\n  2-min cycle = 1/20+1/30 = 1/12\nStep 2: 11 cycles(22min) = 11/12\n  Left=1/12. Min23(A):1/20\n  After 23: 11/12+1/20=58/60, left=2/60=1/30\n  Min24(B): 1/30 at 1/30 rate = 1 min exact\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM(20,30)=60 → A=3/min, B=2/min\n\n  |M1|M2|M3|M4|...|M23|M24|\n  | A| B| A| B|...| A | B |\n  | 3| 2| 3| 2|...| 3 | 2 |\n  |cycle1|cycle2|  12 cycles=60\n\n12 cycles × 2min = 24 min exact\n\nAnswer: 24 minutes ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
