      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1617,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "Pipes A+B fill in 6 hrs, B+C fill in 8 hrs, A+C fill in 12\nhrs. How long for all three together?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
