      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A+B=1/6, B+C=1/8, A+C=1/12\n  Add all: 2(A+B+C) = 1/6+1/8+1/12\n  = 4/24+3/24+2/24 = 9/24 = 3/8\nStep 2: A+B+C = 3/16 → Time = 16/3 hrs\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM(6,8,12)=24 → A+B=4, B+C=3, A+C=2\n2(A+B+C)=9 → A+B+C=4.5/hr\nTime = 24/4.5 = 16/3 = 5h 20m\n\n  A+B=4 ─┐\n  B+C=3 ─┤ sum=9, half=4.5\n  A+C=2 ─┘\n\nAnswer: 5 hours 20 minutes ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
