    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2109,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=+1/12, B=+1/15, C=-1/20\nStep 2: Net = 1/12+1/15-1/20\n  = 5/60+4/60-3/60 = 6/60 = 1/10\nStep 3: Time = 1÷(1/10) = 10 hours\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM(12,15,20)=60 → A=5, B=4, C=-3\nNet = 5+4-3 = 6 units/hr\n\n  A ──→ +5  ──┐\n  B ──→ +4  ──┤──→ 6/hr\n  C ──→ -3  ──┘──→ 60/6 = 10 hrs\n\nAnswer: 10 hours ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 65,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=+1/12, B=+1/15, C=-1/20\nStep 2: Net = 1/12+1/15-1/20\n  = 5/60+4/60-3/60 = 6/60 = 1/10\nStep 3: Time = 1÷(1/10) = 10 hours\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nLCM(12,15,20)=60 → A=5, B=4, C=-3\nNet = 5+4-3 = 6 units/hr\n\n  A ──→ +5  ──┐\n  B ──→ +4  ──┤──→ 6/hr\n  C ──→ -3  ──┘──→ 60/6 = 10 hrs\n\nAnswer: 10 hours ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
